channel.title: Moparisthebest clan first party/outing pictures!
channel.description:
Hey before i get started mods please tell me if its against the rules to post the url, it got accepted before by a mod in a different thread so i don't think it needs re-checking.
www.spiced-fx.com/forums/ is the official moparisthebest clan forum!
Ok the point of this message is to show pictures and get more people to see that this is a true clan that is working, so i am going to post pictures of our first event which had this stuff included:
-Met in varrock centre with about 5 people -Everyone went to my house and me and Ollie both dropped alot of stuff (see pictures) -Then went off to castle wars and played "protect chris" because chris only level 3 on his new account.
Here are the pictures:
[img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/party1.jpg[/img] ^ what i dropped [img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/party2.jpg[/img] ^stuff i dropped on floor.
[img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/Party3.jpg[/img] ^attempts to make a good photo.
[img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/Party4.jpg[/img] ^second attempt
[img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/party5.jpg[/img] ^waiting room at cw
[img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/party6.jpg[/img] ^mr chris running rampant rofl. [img]http://i125.photobucket.com/albums/p80/davidude36/Runescape%20clan/party7.jpg[/img] ^ and finally me getting owned and shortly after logging out.
So what are you waiting for? Join the moparisthebest clan and recieve your own mudkip*
*mudkip not included.
